UAT Feedback & Sign-Off

Please complete testing using the agreed UAT checklist.
Send feedback by email only, so issues are captured in one place.
Keep feedback short and specific: site/page, issue, expected result, screenshot if useful.
Do not request new development or design changes during UAT.
This environment will be refreshed from Production at migration.
Once testing is complete, email confirmation that your area has been tested.
Your email confirmation will be treated as UAT sign-off.
